# RastaConnect/backend/test-api.http

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3001/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test Driver",
  "email": "driver@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}


###
### Login to get a token
POST http://localhost:3001/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "driver@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}


###
### Offer a Ride (PROTECTED)
# You MUST copy the token from the login response and paste it below
POST http://localhost:3001/api/rides
Content-Type: application/json
x-auth-token: PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "origin": "Mumbai",
  "destination": "Pune",
  "departureTime": "2025-09-16T09:00:00",
  "availableSeats": 3,
  "price": 500
}

###
### Get All Rides (PUBLIC)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/rides